A database that will track information on 2 levels.

People
  -Their Names
  -ID's within the school system.
  -Courses taken
  -each exam's score in each course.
  -GPA calculator for current semester
  
Courses
  -Teacher name
  -CourseID
  -Course Name
  -Enrolled students
  
A GUI that makes user navigation easy

  1 screen for logging in
  The next screen will show all personal information for the user.  It will be assumed
the user logging in is also the student.  If not student, will be administrator who will 
be able to update necessary information.
  A screen for each of the following, linked by second screen buttons.
    -Enrolled Courses
    -GPA
    
